person.bio: Charles is passionate about communication – in all forms, at all levels – and sees it as fundamental to cooperation and collaboration of any kind. Charles is a DJ, festival producer, sound engineer and mapping freak. He's been mind-mapping for a long time, and also weaving networks and communities, projects and solutions for helping people and the planet. Media creator, broadcaster, archivist and nonprofit director, Charles is based in Zurich, Switzerland.
